{"tid":1154684,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母二寶果汁糖","createTime":"2019-05-14T12:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T16:02:02.000Z","uid":232995,"like":15,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"879807302a70c3c5b42a462191d7dee2ffbe2521","tid":1154684,"uid":232995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t6W7qZ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft6W7qZ0.png&h=4ef42945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見百佳有特價咪買左2條<br />\n好開心開第一粒就橙色即刻食撚左<br />\n之後諗諗下唔多對路<br />\n通常第一粒開橙色 中間成條都係黃色<br />\n呀屌你老尾真係2條都係咁撚樣<br />\n係唔撚係on9嫁 開2條得5粒橙色<br />\n係咪食檸檬食撚到上撚左腦呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 次次買2寶都剩係食橙色 有剩果d比曬我老母食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ac094355c87a3f04642ca9ee0149804dfe69db","tid":1154684,"uid":118295,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"又嚟世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 檸檬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8084f08d229ceaffdef2d2719bf826055ad741","tid":1154684,"uid":249885,"like":6,"dislike":19,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:42:30.000Z","msg":"狗先食二寶 啲汁奇撚怪怪完全唔好食"},{"pid":"5e50c7f1b8172f9dfa21cfad21143cd559b49b72","tid":1154684,"uid":216749,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:43:40.000Z","msg":"最愛🍋味"},{"pid":"b2897eb0e1c11b8f5e4fd49782026438d42f1784","tid":1154684,"uid":39274,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:44:07.000Z","msg":"比曬檸檬味我"},{"pid":"0007ff67f7eb75709f6e0c38b1e665a66741461d","tid":1154684,"uid":70558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:45:00.000Z","msg":"檸檬味咪幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno